&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master’s degree in Social Work, Counseling, Psychology or other mental health discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independent Licensure required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous supervisory/teaching experience preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience utilizing Electronic Health Record preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in computer technology required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum two years post-graduate experience required and five years strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
